The company was established in 1993. Ever since, grew into a professional, competitive, international, technology, and customer-focused organization. 
SVYDIS GROUP is a dedicated industrial and automotive coating supplier - multi-branded distribution and service company. 
In almost 30 years in the market, the company has grown into an international business that is operating in Baltics, Ukraine, and Kazachstan.

---------------------
Business directions: 
---------------------
✓ Proactive coatings for Building constructions and Oil&Gas industries;
✓ Industrial coatings for Agricultural machinery, public transport, commercial vehicles, railways, sea transport, aviation, and military equipment. 

Svydis strengths and competencies: 
✓ Representation of more than 30 leading brands in refinishing;
✓ Four patented painting technologies;
✓ Export of products and knowledge to more than 10 countries;
✓ Extensive experience in developing professional painting solutions for high-end clients;
✓ Design and installation of auto refinishing body shops and industrial spraying booths;
✓ Provision of all technological and technical support and implementation of processes in paint shops;
✓ Assurance of the highest standards by providing before and after inspections and audits;
✓ Provision of full support, collaboration, training, and certification for staff by skilled coating advisors;
✓ The company has a professional, motivated, empowered team following extensive knowledge and expertise in specific fields and is ready to collaborate with clients. 

For customers: 
⑊ Installations of body shops and industrial painting facilities
⑊ Paints, materials, and equipment for auto refinish and industry

For suppliers: 
⑊  International partnerships with high-end paint manufacturers
⑊  Sales and support of Automotive and Industry paint solutions
⑊  Import/Export of Automotive and Industry painting goods

Core values that we perform with: 
▻ Responsibility
▻ Competence
▻ Creativity
▻ Ethics

Estabelecida em Angola desde 2016, a REDOX ( Ex-QUÍMICA VERDE) é uma das mais eficientes organizações em Angola, com uma reputação estabelecida, estamos comprometidos em fornecer uma ampla gama de reagentes químicos e serviços de testes laboratoriais (monitoramento ambiental e controlo de qualidade).

Nosso portfólio de serviços inclui: 


- Fornecimento de reagentes químicos para análises laboratoriais (água, solo, minerais, etc); 

- Fornecimento de equipamentos de  e vidrarias  para Laboratórios; 

- Serviços de testes Laboratoriais para fins de controlo de Qualidade ou Monitoramento Ambiental:

- Oferecemos treinamento especializado; 

- Oferecemos serviços de tratamento derramamento de produtos químicos e Neutralização de Químicos com data de validade vencida.

Carbonitalia are the suppliers of a Next Generation of Activated Carbon which offer several advantages over “standard” AC:

    - A higher internal surface area for the adsorption/desorption of organic compounds;
    - A higher purity, due to our patented washing process;
    - The lowest CO2 footprint of all offered AC products in the market.

● CHEMABILITY mainly represents European specialty and fine chemicals producers, as well as high-performance industrial minerals;

● CHEMABILITY operate in the leading industrial sectors in Italy and other European Countries as an extended arm on behalf of principal companies, guaranteeing them a high level of professionalism, an authoritative and attentive presence on the territory, as well as collaborative confrontation for the definition of shared objectives and maximum information transparency;

● CHEMABILITY provides a tailored engineered Technical and Commercial Service, observing scrupulous attention to listening and identifying customer needs, formulating the proposal of immediate solutions, or launching customized projects for long-term development or continuous improvement;

